Description: Sinsebeolsik P2 Hangul input method for fcitx5
 Sinsebeolsik P2 (신세벌식 P2) is a three-set Hangul keyboard layout
 with one-key shortcut (galmadeuli) input for selected diphthongs and
 jongseong clusters. This package provides a fcitx5 input method engine
 implementing the layout from a TOML keymap with a hand-rolled state
 machine.
 .
 First-class support is provided for the Totem 38-key split keyboard
 with graceful fallback to standard 60% / TKL / full-size layouts.
 .
 리눅스 fcitx5용 신세벌식 P2 한글 입력기. 토템 38키 분할 키보드를
 일등 시민으로 지원하며, 표준 60% / TKL / 풀사이즈 키보드도 보조
 대상으로 지원합니다.
